          <div class="flex-1 lg:px-20">
            <img
              src="/media/dining7.jpg"
              alt=""
              class="flex-1 w-full aspect-square object-cover rounded-full"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <h2 class="font-bold text-4xl">Culinary Delights</h2>
            <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-justify">
              Savor the flavors of the world at our diverse collection of
              restaurants and bars. From casual poolside dining to romantic
              candlelit dinners, we offer a variety of culinary experiences to
              suit every taste.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="swiper-slide">
        <div class="flex gap-10 lg:gap-32 flex-col lg:flex-row h-full">
          <div class="flex-1 lg:px-20">
            <img
              src="/media/dining5.jpg"
              alt=""
              class="flex-1 w-full aspect-square object-cover rounded-full"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <h2 class="font-bold text-4xl">Signature Cocktails</h2>
            <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-justify">
              Indulge in a refreshing cocktail at one of our stylish bars. From
